The paper discusses the security and performance of mobile web services, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the adaptation of security standards to the mobile domain, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The performance analysis of the mobile host also falls under the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
